00:00:05.313 --> 00:00:10.813
Namaste, I'm Lata Jain.
Welcome to Lata's Kitchen.

00:00:10.890 --> 00:00:14.631
Samai Pulao is a very tasty,
easy and quick to make dish

00:00:15.488 --> 00:00:24.790
Today I'm going to make semai pulao, Lets
see the ingredient required for making it

00:00:24.790 --> 00:00:28.828
For this we'll need

00:00:28.828 --> 00:00:32.049
Roasted Vermicelli - 1 cup

00:00:32.287 --> 00:00:34.560
Water- 2 cups

00:00:34.560 --> 00:00:37.938
Green Peas - 3/4 cup

00:00:37.988 --> 00:00:41.727
Salt - 1 tsp adjust to taste

00:00:41.953 --> 00:00:45.703
Red chilly powder - 1/4 tsp

00:00:45.983 --> 00:00:49.296
Garam Masala Powder - 1/4 tsp

00:00:49.346 --> 00:00:53.023
Carom Seeds - 1/4 tsp

00:00:53.073 --> 00:00:58.309
Clarified Butter or Oil - 1 tbsp

00:00:58.309 --> 00:01:01.311
Green Chilly Sauce  - 1 tbsp

00:01:01.311 --> 00:01:03.578
Asafoetida - 1 pinch

00:01:03.660 --> 00:01:06.098
Turmeric Powder - 1/4 tsp

00:01:06.148 --> 00:01:10.390
Lets start making sevai pulao

00:01:10.390 --> 00:01:22.240
Heat clarified butter
in a heavy bottom pan

00:01:31.227 --> 00:01:34.969
Clarified butter is heated,
now add carom seeds

00:01:38.133 --> 00:01:41.750
Now add asafoetida

00:01:44.320 --> 00:01:50.566
Lower the gas and add green peas

00:02:00.922 --> 00:02:16.806
You can add any other vegetable of your choice
to it like chopped carrot, beans or potatoes

00:02:17.445 --> 00:02:21.523
Saute it

00:02:25.820 --> 00:02:29.758
Now add vermicelli

00:02:29.758 --> 00:02:40.093
I have used pre roasted vermicelli, its
easily available in the market, if you can't

00:02:40.119 --> 00:02:47.391
find the roasted one, you can roast it
yourself in a kadhai till its golden brown

00:02:47.391 --> 00:02:49.969
Keep the gas low while roasting

00:02:52.703 --> 00:02:58.554
Stir it for few minutes

00:03:01.828 --> 00:03:06.610
Now add water

00:03:13.648 --> 00:03:26.113
Add turmeric powder, salt, red chilly
powder and garam masala powder

00:03:26.820 --> 00:03:28.500
Mix well

00:03:44.883 --> 00:03:49.010
Cover it with the lid

00:03:52.766 --> 00:03:57.181
It has boiled once, turn the gas to low

00:04:00.656 --> 00:04:10.063
Let it cook for 10 minutes

00:04:14.821 --> 00:04:19.750
It's been 5 minutes, lets check it

00:04:28.969 --> 00:04:31.625
Gently stir it

00:04:35.305 --> 00:04:38.891
Cover it and let it cook
for another 5 minutes

00:04:43.773 --> 00:04:49.711
Its been 10 minutes

00:05:00.766 --> 00:05:16.633
Semai Pulao is ready, turn off the
gas and take it out into a plate

00:05:25.719 --> 00:05:48.102
Add some chilly sauce to it. You
can add tomato sauce as well.

00:05:51.484 --> 00:05:56.602
Sevai Pulao is ready. Its very tasty.

00:05:56.602 --> 00:06:03.136
You can make it for breakfast
or pack it as tiffin for kids

00:06:03.136 --> 00:06:07.103
You can also serve it as a tea time snack.

00:06:07.103 --> 00:06:10.781
Thanks for watching Sevai Pulao

